item.title: How do I learn how to code rsps?
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

[quote=“Tree, post:16, topic:436339”]It’s a long path to success, young one. Firstly, you will be approached by a small droid named r2d2. This droid will project a short movie on the life of princess diana and how she’s in need of your aid. Frantically, you will seek help. Batman will arrive and inform you that the droid is actually an evil minion that the joker has involved in his evil plot to sink the titanic.

From your desert home in africa, you will escape from district 9 and hop upon the boat of rock. This boat will take you to the titanic in which you will search for a female named rose. Unfortunately, rose has a boyfriend named jack. The key here is to tell jack that you’re a doctor and helped with Jill’s recovery. They’re related in some way or another. You will laugh and cry with this fellow as the emotional bond between you, strengthens. However, you will soon have a falling out over the fall of the Berlin wall and later, the fall of Humpty Dumpty.

The boat will sink despite your attempts to keep it afloat, where an alien ship will pick you up. Emerging from the water, a battle commences between you and a battleship. Rhianna the singer will fire missiles at you. It’s important to remain strong during this time. You and you’re best mate ‘E.T’ will escape and hide with a small boy, who can see dead people.

Then and only then will you be able to code rsps. I wish you luck.[/quote]Was a good read

It’s a long path to success, young one. Firstly, you will be approached by a small droid named r2d2. This droid will project a short movie on the life of princess diana and how she’s in need of your aid. Frantically, you will seek help. Batman will arrive and inform you that the droid is actually an evil minion that the joker has involved in his evil plot to sink the titanic.

From your desert home in africa, you will escape from district 9 and hop upon the boat of rock. This boat will take you to the titanic in which you will search for a female named rose. Unfortunately, rose has a boyfriend named jack. The key here is to tell jack that you’re a doctor and helped with Jill’s recovery. They’re related in some way or another. You will laugh and cry with this fellow as the emotional bond between you, strengthens. However, you will soon have a falling out over the fall of the Berlin wall and later, the fall of Humpty Dumpty.

The boat will sink despite your attempts to keep it afloat, where an alien ship will pick you up. Emerging from the water, a battle commences between you and a battleship. Rhianna the singer will fire missiles at you. It’s important to remain strong during this time. You and you’re best mate ‘E.T’ will escape and hide with a small boy, who can see dead people.

Then and only then will you be able to code rsps. I wish you luck.
